        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Qwen3 TTS VoiceDesign multi-model API provides a powerful framework for generating natural-sounding speech from text, supporting multiple voice models and customization options. This guide focuses on practical integration for experienced API teams, covering key technical aspects to ensure reliability and efficiency in production."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Overview of Qwen3 TTS VoiceDesign Multi-Model API"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Qwen3 TTS VoiceDesign multi-model API is built on the Qwen3_TTS_12Hz_1_7B_VoiceDesign model, optimized for 12Hz audio output with 1.7 billion parameters. It supports multi-model inference, allowing dynamic voice selection and blending. Key features include low-latency synthesis, support for various languages, and fine-grained control over prosody and timbre. Integration requires understanding the API's RESTful endpoints, authentication via API keys, and JSON-based request/response formats."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integration Steps and Best Practices"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To integrate the API, start by obtaining endpoint URLs and API keys from the provider. Use HTTPS for all requests with headers including "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Authorization: Bearer <API_KEY>",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " and "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Content-Type: application/json",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". The primary endpoint is "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "/v1/tts/synthesize",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", accepting POST requests with a JSON body. Below is a compact table of essential parameters:"
